title: NFL Week 14 Picks Against the Spread, Titans-Jaguars Recap (Football 12/07)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Bryant McFadden to break down the Titans-Jaguars TNF game (2:00) and talk about concerns over the Steelers (15:00). Then Pete Prisco and R.J. White hop on to make picks against the spread for every single game on the slate including: Ravens-Chiefs (22:00), Buccaneers-Saints (27:45), Colts-Texans (30:45), Giants-Redskins (35:00), Eagles-Cowboys (40:00), Falcons-Packers (44:00), Rams-Bears (46:00), Steelers-Raiders (50:00),  Broncos-49ers (53:00), Patriots-Dolphins (56:00), Jets-Bills (61:00), Panthers-Browns (63:30), Bengals-Chargers (69:00), Lions-Cardinals (70:30) and Vikings-Steelers (71:00). Finally the guys play a little game of LET'S GET EXOTIC (74:00). 
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
